upsimulator.rules.conditions

Class PriorityCondition

  • java.lang.Object
    • upsimulator.rules.conditions.PriorityCondition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, Condition

    public class PriorityCondition
extends java.lang.Object
implements Condition
    Represent minimum priority condition in P system.

    Priority condition must not be put at the front of any object conditions in multi-thread context. PriorityCondition must be put at the tail of condition's list, or there will be some mistake.

    Author:
    quan
